#: ../twitter-integration.rst:5
msgid ""
"The ``mezzanine.twitter`` application exposes the ability to consume, store,"
" and display your own tweets on your site in an efficient manner, as well as"
" the ability to send tweets when publishing new content to the site."
msgstr ""

